  "detailed_description": "In this cozy and colorful game, the player needs to surpass high scores set in various rigged Arcade Games inhabited by a residing Ghost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore a hand-painted 3D environment blending the childish nature of the Ghost's character with the retro aesthetic of a 1980s Arcade Hall.<br><br>Play the Story or Arcade Mode!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><br>As you progress through the story of the game, the Ghost starts revealing their backstory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Eventually, you as the player help them move on from their unfinished business.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Earn tickets from the Arcade Games to spend them in the Points Shop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade:</h2><br>Get instant access to all Arcade Games to compete with other players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Us:</h2><br>We are Game Development Students from the University of Applied Sciences Darmstadt, Germany.<br><br>Currently, we are 8 people on the internal team, and 2 sound-students, working on four new Arcade Games simultaneously while also patching up the current game and working on other features and content updates.",
  "about_the_game": "In this cozy and colorful game, the player needs to surpass high scores set in various rigged Arcade Games inhabited by a residing Ghost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8101e9b4c6e038f3dc78fa8dc6cfdbae.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore a hand-painted 3D environment blending the childish nature of the Ghost's character with the retro aesthetic of a 1980s Arcade Hall.<br><br>Play the Story or Arcade Mode!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><br>As you progress through the story of the game, the Ghost starts revealing their backstory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/ad5edea4a7fce1d33fdbf445a7a133f0.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Eventually, you as the player help them move on from their unfinished business.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=338 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/e175d6e5581e8fa883c093d7f3ea16c1.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Earn tickets from the Arcade Games to spend them in the Points Shop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.poster.avif?t=1755004015\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.webm?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/8cec3640989021a261f7d1a13ae948e1.mp4?t=1755004015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade:</h2><br>Get instant access to all Arcade Games to compete with other players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Us:</h2><br>We are Game Development Students from the University of Applied Sciences Darmstadt, Germany.<br><br>Currently, we are 8 people on the internal team, and 2 sound-students, working on four new Arcade Games simultaneously while also patching up the current game and working on other features and content updates.",
